{"type": "article", "id": 26722, "title": "为牛仔裤设计的衣架", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-12T06:39:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 68, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702115739tQkYW4Xs7pnIPGjJ.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">丹宁爱好者们，如果你为如何正确收藏和保养牛仔裤犯愁，不妨试试加拿大产品设计师 Steven Sal Debus 设计的 Jean Hanger。这个牛仔裤专用衣架由坚固细木制成，不同于普通衣架的长度（19 英寸，约合 48 厘米）能够撑起大部分尺寸的牛仔裤，而且中间的钩形部分能够彻底将裤子展平，杜绝了出现褶皱的可能。目前这款衣架在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/saldebus/the-jean-hanger-the-new-way-to-care-for-your-jeans\">Kickstarter</a> 上的众筹还在继续，唯一可惜的是不能寄往中国。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021157372NTCidvKe59zRQYb.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.66627635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115738QR3bnthvcO2u0yoK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115738TgBD20vlfm81WR9r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702115739CgvOWatYroALjTyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}